OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FHome insurer Aviva says accidents are
OL,7,Fa growing problem, leading to scorched
OL,8,Fworktops, smoking appliances, and even
OL,9,Ffull-on house fires, as Consumer
OL,10,FEditor Chris Choi explains
OL,12,FClaims for damage relating to air
OL,13,Ffryers are running into tens of
OL,14,Fthousands of pounds on average, with
OL,15,Fcosts running as high as #80,000, an
OL,16,Finsurance giant is warning.
