OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FAviva said it has seen some
OL,7,Fsignificant home insurance claims
OL,8,Frelating to air fryer fires over the
OL,9,Fpast four years, with claimants
OL,10,Fsustaining considerable fire and smoke
OL,11,Fdamage to their homes.
OL,13,FThe average claim for 2024 amounted to
OL,14,F#29,555 and in one case dealt with by
OL,15,Fthe insurer, an air fryer fire caused
OL,16,F#80,000 worth of damage to a kitchen
OL,17,Fafter spreading and setting the entire
OL,18,Froom alight, destroying the kitchen
OL,19,Fceiling, walls, cupboards and their
OL,20,Fcontents, a washing machine and a
OL,21,Ftelevision.
