OL,11,FAviva said that in some cases,
OL,12,Fclaimants have described seeing flames
OL,13,Ferupting from collapsing and melting
OL,14,Fair fryers, destroying the surfaces on
OL,15,Fwhich they were placed.
OL,17,FIt has also dealt with several claims
OL,18,Fwhere air fryers had been placed on
OL,19,Fhobs, accidentally switching the hob
OL,20,Fon and inadvertently setting the air
OL,21,Ffryer ablaze.
