OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FIn one incident, a hungry dog was
OL,7,Fresponsible for a hob being
OL,8,Faccidentally switched on.
OL,10,FThe insurer also commissioned a survey
OL,11,Fby Censuswide, which found that around
OL,12,Ftwo-thirds (68%) of people in the
OL,13,Fresearch own an air fryer.
OL,15,FNearly a fifth (19%) of people
OL,16,Fsurveyed said they had encountered
OL,17,Fpotential or actual fire hazards in
OL,18,Ftheir homes because of one, such as
OL,19,Fsmoke, overheating or scorching.
