OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FThe research also indicated that many
OL,7,Fpeople do not always follow guidelines
OL,8,Fand advice when using their air fryer,
OL,9,Fwith only around a fifth (21%) saying
OL,10,Fthey strictly follow the manual
OL,11,Fprovided with their item.
OL,13,FSome people in the survey admitted to
OL,14,Fregularly over-filling their air fryer
OL,15,Fand some used it in a non-ventilated
OL,16,Farea such as a cupboard, according to
OL,17,Fthe survey of 2,000 people in December.
